job_description:
• Conduct full sales cycle for international customers, from initial contact to contract negotiation and closing;
• Coordinate with relevant departments for completion of administrative sales service such as contract preparing, shipment logistics etc;
• Look for new customers & take care assigned customers; build and maintain good relationships with clients as well as partners in Pulp & Paper industry to ensure continuous business growth and ability to create win-win situations;
• Achieve or exceed sales quotas for assigned territories;
• Analyze, identify trends in global markets to identify suitable sales channels and pricing for business development;
• Take part in conferences of Pulp & Paper/Packaging industry;
• Daily, weekly and monthly monitoring and updating of sales activities or other market reports when requested;
• Management of debt collection system and program to ensure low level of outstanding debt ratio.
